In a tweet, the minister said, he had full faith that Election Commission of Pakistan (ECP) will discharge its duties to ensure free and fair Cantonment Board Elections  according to its mandate under article 218(3) of constitution.
The minister said, however, he was surprised to receive a show cause notice as he had not been in the constituency since elections were announced.
